Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(0,500)}你這娘們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(500,500)}我叫花京院典明 昨天剛轉學到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}這東西…像是鋼筆嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,710)}敗者即是邪惡
Comment: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:42.48,title_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\pos(640,606)}由誰裁決！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁決你的人…
